snippet.title: Super Mario Galaxy 64 Holiday Special
snippet.description:
This is a demo for the SMG2 hack I'm working on called Super Mario Galaxy 64. It contains three winter themed levels. If you've played Super Mario 64 or Super Mario 64 DS, you should be very familiar with these levels. Regardless if you've played these games or not, there are secrets and exploration waiting in every level.

DOWNLOAD
https://www.mediafire.com/file/j1d2ra2mi3uryea/SMG64_Holiday_Special_v1.1.zip/file
